## License Overview

This repository contains proprietary source code, documentation, design assets, and related materials ("Codebase") developed and maintained by Absheron Logistic Center Subsidiaries for the Absheron Career Center platform (https://career.absheronport.az/), a strategic HR recruitment and vacancy management solution supporting Absheron Logistic Center's workforce development initiatives.

The Codebase is licensed under the MIT License with specific additional provisions outlined herein to ensure proper usage aligned with Absheron Logistic Center’s corporate compliance, security, and ethical standards.

